                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090920-157-victim1524 t18090920-157-viclabel919"></join>. On the 1st of September my wife thought she heard somebody up stairs on the second floor, I went up stairs with her, and found the prisoner in the bed room, the bed clothes were very much disordered, the pillows and blankets were laying about the room, and likewise in the adjoining room; my wife saw him first lay under the bed in the second room; we found him three parts of the way out of the second floor window, so that the whole of his body was hanging out, his legs only appeared, I pulled him back.</p>
               <p>Q. What is he - A. He gave me to understand that he had a share in an hackney coach.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18090920-157-person1526">
                  JOHN 
                  BAKER
               <interp inst="t18090920-157-person1526" type="surname" value="BAKER"></interp>
